title: Deer Tick "White Havoc"
description:
“White Havoc” is the first single bringing holiday cheer from Converse Rubber Tracks’ holiday music EP, Noise To the World 2. Deer Tick recorded and mixed this original composition at their studio in Providence, RI. 

Produced and mixed by: Deer Tick
Music and Lyrics By: Deer Tick
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman
